Package com.bws.jdistil.core.configuration

Interface Summary
IConfiguration Interface supporting the definition of application configurations.
 

Class Summary
Action Class defining action configuration information.
ActionIds Class defining all core action IDs.
AttributeNames Class defining all core attribute names.
Configuration Abstract base class used by applications to define configuration.
ConfigurationManager Configuration manager used by core framework classes to retrieve action, field, page, and object binding related information.
Constants Class defining all system level constants.
Field Class defining field configuration information.
FieldBinding Defines a binding between a field ID and the property name of an object.
FieldIds Class defining all core field IDs.
FieldValues Class defining all field values used by the core frameworks classes.
ObjectBinding Defines a binding between the properties of a target class and field IDs.
Page Class defining page specific information.
PageIds Class defining all core page IDs.
ServletNames Class defining all registered servlet names used by the core framework classes.
SystemConfiguration Configuration responsible for loading framework dependent application resources.
 

Exception Summary
ConfigurationException Package level exception defined as a base exception for the configuration package.
